---
import EmpaqueMediano from "../../public/empaques/mediana.webp";
import EmpaqueGrande from "../../public/empaques/grande.webp";
import EmpaqueEspecial from "../../public/empaques/especial.webp";
---

<section
    id="presentaciones"
    class="w-full flex mb-25 flex-col gap-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 scroll-my-20"
>
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary">
        Empaques para cada necesidad
    </h1>
    <div class="flex h-full w-full flex-col gap-12 md:gap-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-15">
            <div
                data-animate="fade-right"
                class="group order-1 relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-background p-8 text-purple-300 md:order-none md:p-12"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-16 -left-16 z-0 h-[140%] w-2/3 rotate-12 bg-purple-300/25 rounded-[90px] transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:rotate-[20deg]"
                >
                </div>
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute top-3 left-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 -rotate-12 opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-rotate-6 md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 rotate-[160deg] opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[166deg] md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 z-2 h-3 w-2/5 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/20 blur-md md:bottom-8 md:h-4"
                >
                </div>
                <img
                    src={EmpaqueEspecial.src}
                    class="relative z-3 w-full rounded-md transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]"
                    alt="Vela especial de Velas Montenegro"
                />
            </div>
            <div
                data-animate="fade-left"
                data-animate-delay="0.1"
                class="order-2 flex flex-col gap-2 justify-center text-center md:order-none md:text-left"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
                    La Especial, para ocasiones que lo merecen
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg">
                    Pensada para procesiones, velaciones y ceremonias
                    especiales: mayor tamaño y mayor tiempo de combustión para
                    acompañar los momentos más importantes sin apagarse antes de
                    tiempo.
                </p>
                <button
                    data-cotizar="especial"
                    class="mt-2 w-fit self-center px-5 py-2 font-medium text-lg bg-primary text-white rounded-sm md:self-start"
                    >Cotizar</button
                >
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-15">
            <div
                data-animate="fade-right"
                class="order-2 flex flex-col gap-2 justify-center text-center md:order-none md:text-left"
            >
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center md:justify-start"
                >
                    <span
                        class="order-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white sm:order-2"
                        >Más elegida</span
                    >
                    <h2
                        class="order-2 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold sm:order-1"
                    >
                        La Grande, para alumbrar espacios más amplios
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg">
                    La mejor opción cuando se necesita mayor volumen: iglesias,
                    negocios y eventos que requieren varias velas encendidas por
                    varias horas seguidas, sin perder calidad ni consistencia en
                    la cera.
                </p>
                <button
                    data-cotizar="grande"
                    class="mt-2 w-fit self-center px-5 py-2 font-medium text-lg bg-primary text-white rounded-sm md:self-start"
                    >Cotizar</button
                >
            </div>
            <div
                data-animate="fade-left"
                data-animate-delay="0.1"
                class="group order-1 relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-background p-8 text-blue-300 ring-2 ring-primary/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:ring-primary/50 md:order-none md:p-12"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-16 -left-16 z-0 h-[140%] w-2/3 rotate-12 bg-blue-300/25 rounded-[90px] transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:rotate-[20deg]"
                >
                </div>
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute top-3 left-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 -rotate-12 opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-rotate-6 md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 rotate-[160deg] opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[166deg] md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 z-2 h-3 w-2/5 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/20 blur-md md:bottom-8 md:h-4"
                >
                </div>
                <img
                    src={EmpaqueGrande.src}
                    class="relative z-3 w-full rounded-md transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]"
                    alt="Vela grande de Velas Montenegro"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-15">
            <div
                data-animate="fade-right"
                class="group order-1 relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-background p-8 text-red-300 md:order-none md:p-12"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-16 -left-16 z-0 h-[140%] w-2/3 rotate-12 bg-red-300/25 rounded-[90px] transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:rotate-[20deg]"
                >
                </div>
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute top-3 left-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 -rotate-12 opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-rotate-6 md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <svg
                    viewBox="0 0 100 140"
                    class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 z-1 h-16 w-12 rotate-[160deg] opacity-70 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[166deg] md:h-20 md:w-15"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    ><path
                        d="M50 12 C32 36 22 60 28 82 C32 98 42 110 50 122 C58 110 68 98 72 82 C78 60 68 36 50 12 Z"
                    ></path><path
                        d="M50 55 C41 70 39 88 50 102 C61 88 59 70 50 55 Z"
                        stroke-width="2"></path><circle
                        cx="70"
                        cy="25"
                        r="4"
                        fill="currentColor"></circle></svg
                >
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 z-2 h-3 w-2/5 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/20 blur-md md:bottom-8 md:h-4"
                >
                </div>
                <img
                    src={EmpaqueMediano.src}
                    class="relative z-3 w-full rounded-md transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]"
                    alt="Vela mediana de Velas Montenegro"
                />
            </div>
            <div
                data-animate="fade-left"
                data-animate-delay="0.1"
                class="order-2 flex flex-col gap-2 justify-center text-center md:order-none md:text-left"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
                    La Mediana, el equilibrio perfecto para el día a día
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg">
                    A diferencia de la Especial, pensada para ocasiones
                    puntuales, la Mediana ofrece una duración igual de confiable
                    a un precio más accesible: ideal para el uso diario en el
                    hogar, negocios y altares.
                </p>
                <button
                    data-cotizar="mediana"
                    class="mt-2 w-fit self-center px-5 py-2 font-medium text-lg bg-primary text-white rounded-sm md:self-start"
                    >Cotizar</button
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
